Returns a list of platform users which has an access to the board 

### HTTP Request

`GET /boards/<ID>/users`

### Available Parameters

Parameter | Description
--------- | -----------
all | (bool) Show all available users or only with roles. Default false.
issue_count | (bool) Return issue_count field. Default false.

### Expand Parameters

Parameter | Description
--------- | -----------
user | [User model](#get-user)


## Board User Creation

This endpoint creates a new role user.

### HTTP Request

`POST /boards/<ID>/users` 

### Available Parameters

Parameter | Description
--------- | -----------
platform_user_id | User ID
role_id | Role ID

## Board User Deleting

This endpoint removes an exist role user.

### HTTP Request

`DELETE /BOARDS/<BOARD_ID>/users/<PLATFORM_USER_ID>`

### Available Parameters

Parameter | Description
--------- | -----------
platform_user_id | User ID 